<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />Who is the man who fears Yahweh?</para>

<para style="q1">The Lord will instruct him in the way that he should choose.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />His life will go along in goodness;</para>

<para style="q1">and his descendants will inherit the land.</para>
